::Orchestra/Composer::

        Orchestra smiled as he saw the bot he met before.

         "Yes, all enemies shall tremble with fear when they hear the bold
tune of the Predacons!!!" Orchestra shouted out in his new Predacon glory.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
        Composer nodded.  He was wondering what to think of first.

         "Hey, I'm still debating on another strategy that may dramatically
improve the defence systems, but until I can get it clear, do you by any
chance have submarinal weapons?  See, I wonder if we can add hidden lasers
underwater to protect from deep-sea assaults.  Until I think of my full
master plan, that's all I can think of," He said, pacing.
